    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1metrics_1_1MeterConfig" kindref="compound">MeterConfig</ref> defines various configurable aspects of a Meter&apos;s behavior. This class should not be used directly to configure a Meter&apos;s behavior, instead a ScopeConfigurator should be used to compute the desired <ref refid="classopentelemetry_1_1sdk_1_1metrics_1_1MeterConfig" kindref="compound">MeterConfig</ref> which can then be used to configure a Meter. </para>
